verses.text_plain: Give unto the Lord, O ye mighty, give unto the Lord glory and strength.
verses.verse_html:
1Give unto the Lord, O ye mighty, give unto the Lord glory and strength. ▼
▼ ye mighty: Heb. ye sons of the mighty

footnotes.body_text: ▼ ye mighty: Heb. ye sons of the mighty
footnotes.body_html: ▼ ye mighty: Heb. ye sons of the mighty

verses.text_plain: Give unto the Lord the glory due unto his name; worship the Lord in the beauty of holiness.
verses.verse_html:
2Give unto the Lord the glory due unto his name; worship the Lord in the beauty of holiness. ▼
▼ the glory…: Heb. the honour of his name
 , ▼
▼ in…: or, in his glorious sanctuary

footnotes.body_text: ▼ the glory…: Heb. the honour of his name
footnotes.body_html: ▼ the glory…: Heb. the honour of his name

footnotes.body_text: ▼ in…: or, in his glorious sanctuary
footnotes.body_html: ▼ in…: or, in his glorious sanctuary

verses.text_plain: The voice of the Lord is upon the waters: the God of glory thundereth: the Lord is upon many waters.
verses.verse_html:
3The voice of the Lord is upon the waters: the God of glory thundereth: the Lord is upon many waters. ▼
▼ many: or, great

verses.text_plain: The voice of the Lord is powerful; the voice of the Lord is full of majesty.
verses.verse_html:
4The voice of the Lord is powerful; the voice of the Lord is full of majesty. ▼
▼ powerful: Heb. in power
 , ▼
▼ full…: Heb. in majesty

footnotes.body_html: ▼ powerful: Heb. in power
▼ full…: Heb. in majesty

verses.text_plain: The voice of the Lord breaketh the cedars; yea, the Lord breaketh the cedars of Lebanon.
verses.verse_html: 5The voice of the Lord breaketh the cedars; yea, the Lord breaketh the cedars of Lebanon.

verses.text_plain: He maketh them also to skip like a calf; Lebanon and Sirion like a young unicorn.
verses.verse_html: 6He maketh them also to skip like a calf; Lebanon and Sirion like a young unicorn.

tokens.text: He maketh them also to skip

verses.text_plain: The voice of the Lord divideth the flames of fire.
verses.verse_html:
7The voice of the Lord divideth the flames of fire. ▼
▼ divideth: Heb. cutteth out

footnotes.body_html: ▼ divideth: Heb. cutteth out

verses.text_plain: The voice of the Lord shaketh the wilderness; the Lord shaketh the wilderness of Kadesh.
verses.verse_html: 8The voice of the Lord shaketh the wilderness; the Lord shaketh the wilderness of Kadesh.

verses.text_plain: The voice of the Lord maketh the hinds to calve, and discovereth the forests: and in his temple doth every one speak of his glory.
verses.verse_html:
9The voice of the Lord maketh the hinds to calve, and discovereth the forests: and in his temple doth every one speak of his glory. ▼
▼ to calve: or, to be in pain
 , ▼
▼ doth…: or, every whit of it uttereth, etc

footnotes.body_text: ▼ to calve: or, to be in pain
footnotes.body_html: ▼ to calve: or, to be in pain

footnotes.body_text: ▼ doth…: or, every whit of it uttereth, etc
footnotes.body_html: ▼ doth…: or, every whit of it uttereth, etc

verses.text_plain: The Lord sitteth upon the flood; yea, the Lord sitteth King for ever.
verses.verse_html: 10The Lord sitteth upon the flood; yea, the Lord sitteth King for ever.

verses.text_plain: The Lord will give strength unto his people; the Lord will bless his people with peace.
verses.verse_html: 11The Lord will give strength unto his people; the Lord will bless his people with peace.
